title: Error: No training data provided.
body:
Good afternoon,

I tried to run the program but I keep getting the same error continuously,
I reinstalled my Windows 11 to see if that was the issue, and even tried it with Windows 8 and 10.
But I keep getting this error, it would be really nice if there is a solution for it.

could it be that my system is not good??
I have a computer with the parts:

CPU:          AMD Ryzen Threadripper 2990WX 32-Core Processor
RAM:         128 GB
GPU:          NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2080 Ti
SSD:          GIGABYTE GP-AG42TB (2TB)
